dc_title_s: West Indies, Cuba--south coast, Punta San Jose to Manzanillo (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. "From Cuban charts to 1975." "Copyright 1996 by the United States government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Inset: Port of Guayabal. Scale 1:20,000. Includes compilation diagram. Map NO.27207 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
